{"tid":10822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為遷就班中國大媽，「香港寬頻」被改名為「香港寬帶」！","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T06:16:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1748fc68d7e26e256e80fb72161585da0604943","tid":10822,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"【迎戰深港通】怕大媽唔識&hellip;香港寬頻被改名「香港寬帶」<br />\n<br />\n2016-11-29 11:48:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中港矛盾，文化差異，喺「深港通」之下進一步淡化！點解咁講，話說上星期深交所公佈深股通股票暫定名單，作為一個炒友，係咁而都要碌下張List。但睇到中間，你會發現有一間公司，喺中港融合之下被改名！股票編號1310，即係「香港寬頻」，冇錯啦！但喺名單下，你會見到佢個名，竟然係&hellip;竟然係&hellip;「香港寬帶」！<br />\n<br />\n媽呀！如果係咁，咁點解「數碼通」（315）唔使改做「數字通」？就算內地人唔知咩係「寬頻」，夾硬轉個名叫「香港寬帶」&hellip;對內地投資者來講，上網Search「香港寬帶」就得個吉，投資前點做功課？神奇！頂級！超卓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55979885&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55979885%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6c33aa81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55979885%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=4e8126c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55979885&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"2773365d31274e4446cfefc975f1fdeccc405f49","tid":10822,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"係咪被迫改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b848f16cceaeeaf117e1c235bca56d27aaf7cc5c","tid":10822,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:50:43.000Z","msg":"叫白帶呀麻"},{"pid":"3249f074915d37a3f972d223ac2d3a161ac3e048","tid":10822,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016